document_data.name: Villiam Obarskyr
document_data.mainbody: 'Villiam Obarskyr''' was the younger brother of the first settler to [[Cormyr]], [[Ondeth Obarskyr]].
document_data.Relatives: Villiam's wife was [[Karsha Obarskyr]]. His older brother was [[Ondeth Obarskyr]]. His eldest daughter was [[Medaly Obarskyr]].
